<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tsmḥ lnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tsmḥ lnạ wbkl ḥb nklmk
 nbʿt rsạlẗ fyhạ mʿny̱ bytwṣf
 dh ạ̹lhnạ mạdd ạ̹ydh dạymaⁿạ ysndk
 klmẗ yswʿ mn fmk ạnt bttʿrf
 yạlly btkml ṭryq kạrwz ạldyạr
 mrqs ḥbybk md ạ̹ydh wslmk
 mftạyḥ blạd wsẖʿb ḍd ạlạnhyạr
 zy ạlmlk wạqf wlạ sẖyʾ yhzmk
 ạlqrạr- yạ rạʿynạ wạ̉b lynạ bnḥbk
 bạ̹ymạn qwd ạlsfynẗ bạ̹yd qwyẗ
 bṭrknạ ʿdy bynạ wfy ḥḍnk
 rạḥ nlqy̱ ṣwt yswʿ lynạ hdyẗ
 2- ḥbk ymạmẗ ṭạyrẗ fwq fy ạlsmạ
 tlf blạd mn sẖrqhạ lgẖrbhạ
 fy nạs bʿydẗ wqlwb gẖlbh ạạlʿmy̱
 lkn yswʿ mḥtạj kẖrạfẗ trhạ</lyrics>
